Fractal Syndrome is defined as a new entity by the WHO in 2007.
First symptoms appear in growth areas such as the skin, nails and intestinal lining. It slowly spreads to the iris, teeth and eventually limbs. Transmission occurs through unknown mechanisms. No treatment exists. twitter.com/Valdevia_Art/s…
